"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?32/61/33748/abstract/7\">",
"      Beutler E, Felitti VJ, Koziol JA, et al. Penetrance of 845G--&gt; A (C282Y) HFE hereditary haemochromatosis mutation in the USA. Lancet 2002; 359:211.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
