"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?32/61/33748/abstract/8\">",
"      Cotler SJ, Bronner MP, Press RD, et al. End-stage liver disease without hemochromatosis associated with elevated hepatic iron index. J Hepatol 1998; 29:257.",
"     </a>",
